### âš™ï¸ **Optional: Create a Desktop Shortcut or Alias**

You can add an alias so you donâ€™t have to type the full command each time.

```bash
echo "alias jn='jupyter notebook'" >> ~/.bashrc
source ~/.bashrc
```

Now you can simply run:

```bash
jn
```

